OL,7,FFirst, the good news.
OL,9,Fthan the IMF was expecting a year ago
OL,10,Fand economic growth in 2024 has proved
OL,11,Fstronger.
OL,13,FThe UK economy is now forecast to
OL,14,Fexpand by 0.7% this year (a slight
OL,15,Fupgrade on last month's forecast)
OL,16,Fbefore growth picks up to a more
OL,17,Fnormal-looking 1.5% next year on the
OL,18,Fback of stable price, lower interest
OL,19,Frates and rising household incomes.
