OL,3,CIMF says scrap pensions triple lock
OL,4,Cand warns post-election tax rises are
OL,5,Clikely
OL,7,FThe IMF judges the government's
OL,8,Fexisting spending plans beyond next
OL,9,FMarch to be unrealistic and warns that
OL,10,Fwhichever party triumphs in the
OL,11,Fforthcoming election will likely have
OL,12,Fto either raise taxes or cut spending.
OL,14,FAnd the IMF believes, given the state
OL,15,Fof public services, that tax rises are
OL,16,Fmore probable.
OL,18,FWhoever forms the next government will
OL,19,Fimmediately face what the IMF calls
OL,20,F"tough choices".
