OL,7,FNational debt as a share of GDP has
OL,8,Freached its highest level for 70 years
OL,9,Fand shows no sign of falling; interest
OL,10,Frates and therefore debt interest
OL,11,Fcosts are high; the "Tax Burden" (tax
OL,12,Frevenues measured as a share of
OL,13,Fnational income) has risen and is
OL,14,Fheading to UK record levels; and
OL,15,Fpublic services are visibly under
OL,16,Fstrain.
