OL,3,CIMF says scrap pensions triple lock
OL,4,Cand warns post-election tax rises are
OL,5,Clikely
OL,7,FIn March this year, the Chancellor
OL,8,Funveiled a Budget which delivered tax
OL,9,Fcuts - which are always lovely to have
OL,10,F- predicated on big cuts in public
OL,11,Finvestment spending (necessary to lift
OL,12,Feconomic growth and fund the
OL,13,Ftransition to Net Zero) and cuts to
OL,14,Fspending in many areas of public
OL,15,Fservices beyond 2024/25.
OL,17,FThe IMF has been signalling for a few
OL,18,Fyears that preserving public services
OL,19,Fin the UK and raising public
OL,20,Finvestment would likely require higher
OL,21,Ftaxes.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/13
