OL,3,CIMF says scrap pensions triple lock
OL,4,Cand warns post-election tax rises are
OL,5,Clikely
OL,7,FIn January, it said so explicitly and
OL,8,Fadvised the chancellor against cutting
OL,9,Ftaxes in his Budget. Jeremy Hunt chose
OL,10,Fnot to take that advice. In March, he
OL,11,Fcut National Insurance for a second
OL,12,Ftime in six months and has since said
OL,13,Fhe hopes to reduce it again before the
OL,14,Felection.
OL,16,FThe IMF says the government will find
OL,17,Fit "difficult" to stick to its
OL,18,Fspending plans beyond next year so it
OL,19,Fhas pencilled in spending projections
OL,20,Fof its own.
