OL,3,CIMF says scrap pensions triple lock
OL,4,Cand warns post-election tax rises are
OL,5,Clikely
OL,7,FHelpfully, the IMF recommends ways in
OL,8,Fwhich that money could be raised.
OL,9,FThese include scrapping the Triple-
OL,10,FLock on pensions, broadening the bases
OL,11,Ffor VAT and Inheritance Tax or
OL,12,Freforming capital gains and property
OL,13,Ftaxation.
OL,15,FAs things stand, neither the Tories
OL,16,Fnor Labour is set to make any of these
OL,17,Foptions election pledges.
