OL,7,FThe IMF doesn't offer opinions on what
OL,8,Fpolitical choices should be made, only
OL,9,Fthat choices should made.
OL,11,FIn the circumstances, the IMF repeats
OL,12,Fits view that further tax cuts would
OL,13,Fbe unwise.
OL,15,FThe point here is that, in the IMF's
OL,16,Fview, the current situation is
OL,17,Funsustainable. Something needs to
OL,18,Fgive, the centre cannot hold.
